            <hr>
            <h2>üë®‚Äçüíª Tech</h2>
            <p>HomeKitty is completely open-source on <a href="https://github.com/balestraPatrick/HomeKitty" target="_blank">GitHub</a>. If you want to add a feature or fix a problem, you're welcome to do so.<br>
            It is built on top of <a href="https://github.com/vapor/vapor" target="_blank">Vapor 2</a> and is written completely in Swift.</p>
            <p><a href="https://github.com/vapor-community/stripe" target="_blank">Vapor Stripe Provider</a> is used to process donations via Apple Pay.
            <a href="https://github.com/brokenhandsio/leaf-error-middleware" target="_blank">Leaf Error Middleware</a> is used to customize error pages.</p>

